data.description: Explore this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home nestled in desirable community in Baytown.  Large fenced yard for your fur babies. Brand new carpet throughout with stove, refrigerator, and brand new microwave stay. Enjoy the spacious primary bedroom first floor plus relax in garden tub or separate shower.  Home offers a welcoming entry, high ceilings in the living room and, game room/media room. There is Nuvia water softening & filtration system. Larger back yard for your family gatherings, fully fenced yard. Make your appointment today!!
